trong>+9; <strong>CMD </strong>23</p><p><strong>Feats </strong>Combat Reflexes, Flyby Attack, Hover</p><p><strong>Skills </strong>Acrobatics +4, Fly +12, Perception +10, Stealth +14 (+20 in stony areas), Survival +10</p><p><strong>Languages </strong>Common, Terran</p><p><strong>SQ </strong>freeze</p></div></section>","img":"modules/statblock-library/assets/Covers/Curse_of_the_Crimson_Throne.jpg","_id":"HDjsdIzsjNW3i4Ml"}
