ong>CMB </strong>+10; <strong>CMD </strong>21</p><p><strong>Feats </strong>Alertness, Dazzling Display, Improved Iron Will, Iron Will, Power Attack, Shield Focus, Skill Focus (Intimidate), Weapon Focus (longsword), Weapon Specialization (longsword)</p><p><strong>Skills </strong>Intimidate +13, Perception +10, Sense Motive +3</p><p><strong>Languages </strong>Common</p><p><strong>SQ </strong>armor training 2</p><p><strong>Combat Gear </strong><i>potion of cure moderate wounds</i>; <strong>Other Gear </strong><i>+1 full plate</i>, mwk heavy steel shield, <i>+1 longsword</i>, composite longbow (+3 Str) with 20 arrows, 16 pp, 5 gp</p></div></section>","img":"modules/statblock-library/assets/Covers/Curse_of_the_Crimson_Throne.jpg","_id":"flmFoQnVWOqb7GR9"}
